title: rust asserts on FreeBSD 13 i386 while compiling diskonaut-0.11.0: Failed assertion: "tcache_success == (ret != NULL)"
body:
```
   Compiling cassowary v0.3.0
     Running `/usr/local/bin/rustc --crate-name cassowary /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/diskonaut-0.11.0/cargo-crates/cassowary-0.3.0/src/lib.rs --error-format=json --json=diagnostic-rendered-ansi,artifacts --crate-type lib --emit=dep-info,metadata,link -C opt-level=2 -Cembed-bitcode=no -C metadata=fd7cd96b62e7f2f2 -C extra-filename=-fd7cd96b62e7f2f2 --out-dir /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps -L dependency=/wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps --cap-lints allow -C linker=cc -C link-arg=-fstack-protector-strong`
   Compiling filesize v0.2.0
     Running `/usr/local/bin/rustc --crate-name filesize --edition=2018 /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/diskonaut-0.11.0/cargo-crates/filesize-0.2.0/src/lib.rs --error-format=json --json=diagnostic-rendered-ansi --crate-type lib --emit=dep-info,metadata,link -C opt-level=2 -Cembed-bitcode=no -C metadata=33f7b5dbbcd145ff -C extra-filename=-33f7b5dbbcd145ff --out-dir /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps -L dependency=/wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps --cap-lints allow -C linker=cc -C link-arg=-fstack-protector-strong`
<jemalloc>: /usr/local/poudriere/jails/head-i386/usr/src/contrib/jemalloc/include/jemalloc/internal/tcache_inlines.h:52: Failed assertion: "tcache_success == (ret != NULL)"
error: could not compile `filesize`.

Caused by:
  process didn't exit successfully: `/usr/local/bin/rustc --crate-name filesize --edition=2018 /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/diskonaut-0.11.0/cargo-crates/filesize-0.2.0/src/lib.rs --error-format=json --json=diagnostic-rendered-ansi --crate-type lib --emit=dep-info,metadata,link -C opt-level=2 -Cembed-bitcode=no -C metadata=33f7b5dbbcd145ff -C extra-filename=-33f7b5dbbcd145ff --out-dir /wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps -L dependency=/wrkdirs/usr/ports/sysutils/diskonaut/work/target/release/deps --cap-lints allow -C linker=cc -C link-arg=-fstack-protector-strong` (signal: 6, SIGABRT: process abort signal)
warning: build failed, waiting for other jobs to finish...
error: build failed
*** Error code 101
```
